text: Miglena Angelova Mikhaleva (; born 1 August 1968) is a Bulgarian rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ruse, Bulgaria
